qas.question: What is the name of the section of the Saturday edition of The Times that features travel and lifestyle?
Arts, books, and ideas are featured in what section in the Saturday edition of The Times?
An entertainment listings guide in the Saturday edition of The Times is called what?

context: The Saturday edition of The Times contains a variety of supplements. These supplements were relaunched in January 2009 as: Sport, <a0_0>Weekend<a0_0/> (including travel and lifestyle features), <a1_0>Saturday Review<a1_0/> (arts, books, and ideas), The Times Magazine (columns on various topics), and <a2_0>Playlist<a2_0/> (an entertainment listings guide).
